<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About Genderbase</h1>

  <div class="prose lg:prose-xl max-w-4xl">
    <p class="mb-4">Genderbase is a community-driven platform dedicated to providing accurate, supportive information about gender identity, expression, and diversity. Our mission is to create a safe space where people can learn about gender,and find answers to their questions.</p>

    <p class="mb-4">Founded in 2025 by <a href="https://dave.io">Dave Williams</a>, Genderbase aims to bridge the knowledge gap that often exists around issues of gender and provide resources that are accessible to everyone.</p>

    <p class="mb-4">Read our <%= link_to "Good Faith policy", home_good_faith_path, class: "text-base-content/80 hover:text-accent transition" %> to understand how we handle questions.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Our Values</h2>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>Respect:</strong> We honor all gender identities and expressions without judgment.</li>
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>Grace:</strong> We answer questions posed in good faith without judgment, even if they may accidentally offend.</li>
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>Accuracy:</strong> We are committed to providing factual, unbiased information.</li>
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>Inclusivity:</strong> We strive to make our platform accessible and welcoming to people from all backgrounds.</li>
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>Community:</strong> We believe in the power of shared knowledge and experiences.</li>
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>Privacy:</strong> We respect user privacy and maintain confidentiality.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">What We Offer</h2>

    <p class="mb-4">Genderbase offers &mdash;</p>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
      <li class="mb-2">A Q&A platform where users can ask questions about gender and receive thoughtful, informed responses.</li>
      <li class="mb-2">A knowledge base with resources on gender-related topics, derived from previously answered questions.</li>
      <li class="mb-2">A comprehensive terminology guide for simple questions of language.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mb-4">We believe that understanding gender diversity is essential for creating a more inclusive and accepting society. By providing accurate information and fostering meaningful dialogue, we hope to make things better for everyone.</p>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <%= link_to "Meet Our Team", home_team_path, class: "btn btn-primary mr-4" %>
      <%= link_to "Get Involved", home_volunteer_path, class: "btn btn-outline" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>